snippet.title: Nom Nom: Cozy Forest Café | Teaser Trailer | Wishlist NOW on Steam!
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2428800/Nom_Nom_Cozy_Forest_Caf/

Learn more about the game:
https://nomnomgame.cafe/
____________________________________
Ever wanted to escape the frenzy of city life? [b]Nom Nom: Cozy Forest Café[/b] is a cozy and relaxed decoration and rhythm game where you manage a cafeteria and befriend cute animals.

Prepare your dishes to the beat of catchy tunes and explore creativity through design in this low-stress experience, creating delightful snacks and beverages.

Form friendships with the customers to unlock new foods and decoration items, and build the cozy forest café of your dreams.

Use your camera to take snapshots of your friends, cafeteria, and food creations and showcase your favorite pictures on the website.
____________________________________
